pologises-jewish-community-antisemitic-comments-3563267">向犹太社区道歉</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-says-kanye-west-fucked-with-the-wrong-jew-this-time-3585447">莎朗·奥斯本 (Sharon Osbourne) 称坎耶·维斯特 (Kanye West) “这次和错误的犹太人上床了”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
