e.com/news/music/watch-the-cure-debut-another-devastating-new-song-i-can-never-say-goodbye-3332974">《I Can Never Say Goodbye》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-cure-debut-heartfelt-new-song-a-fragile-thing-in-italy-3343340">《A Fragile Thing》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-classic-live-album-paris-3585238">The Cure 宣布经典现场专辑《Paris》30 周年再版的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
